Reasoning: The paper discusses the application of filter bank multicarrier (FBMC) in massive MIMO communication, which falls under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), communication (cs.COMM), systems and control (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper specifically focuses on the advantages of FBMC over OFDM in the context of massive MIMO, which is a topic of interest in these sub-categories.
